title: Zendaya Has Priceless Reaction To Finding Out Venus Williams Was At The ‘Challengers’ Premiere In LA | Access
text: Zendaya Has Priceless Reaction To Finding Out Venus Williams Was At The ‘Challengers’ Premiere In LA Zendaya was visibly shook when she found out tennis pro Venus Williams was in attendance Tuesday night at the Los Angeles premiere for her latest movie “Challengers.” The actor talks about what it was like to work with co-stars Mike Faist and Josh O’Connor and who of the three was the class clown on set. Zendaya also reveals she tapped into her dancing skills to perfect her performance playing a tennis prodigy in the film, and discusses it was like working as a producer on the project. Plus, learn about how she and stylist Law Roach have found inspiration for the dazzling looks she has worn on the film’s press tour. “Challengers” hits theaters on April 26.
